Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说阿姆斯特朗少将与雷文中将的失踪有关联？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不会干留下证据的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢 我们的工作只是掌握这要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁那女狐狸在中央被虎群包围的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是少将阁下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 没想到你竟会在中央当差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了什么后门？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是靠实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛头小子真是大言不惭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今日来是有何要事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统阁下叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定暂时回不了北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有机会务必和我吃个便饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你请客？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到你破产也无所谓我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 真是没胆又没钱的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我送您点花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央有很多不错的花店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:02:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 阿姆斯特朗少将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问一下雷文中将失踪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是瞒不了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下您这样贤明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何身边会有那样粗心大意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就把他收拾掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不需要那种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种口风不紧的人对阁下没好处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将对你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死的军团 我国的成立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及阁下的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没问 他就自顾自全说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听了这些话还乖乖来见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是来接收那白痴的位子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 这个位子就给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 布里格斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我的手下接管了 可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里都是我精心培育的精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下一定会满意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中意你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力挣扎吧 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少将亲自入了虎穴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这里也被他们占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他们还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使主君不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然是团结在同一意志下行动的一枚巨石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是布里格斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下来就是熊虎之争了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近来工作还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙得连吃饭时都得努力赶工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要学的东西很多 还算比较忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过幸好阁下工作速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是不会偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来话题走向不大愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说斯卡现在去北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔利克兄弟也在北方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方有和我同期的露茜和伊安在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们告诉我不少消息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 记得春天北方军和东方军有联合演习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 迈尔斯少校和巴卡尼亚上尉总让我们吃败仗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯 巴卡尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约克 艾达 修格都受邀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勃克 奥斯卡 迈克 尤尼 诺拉 查理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又是尤尼和露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着尤尼 最后是斯塔林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞利姆·布拉德雷是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么不可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央到底在搞什么阴谋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能稍微吃惊一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊了你给我什么好处？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 胆子够大这点我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是问号码 问你真正的名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦 我是奴隶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴隶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有权利和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被视为所有物让渡买卖的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让渡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把财产 权利等物转让给他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是你这种人让我诞生的 真想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你吗 给我血的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来好像是要做实验 被抽了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你给的血液 我才能降生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…叫23号还是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你起个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢帅气一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥…迪奥弗拉斯托斯·波姆巴斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太长啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？哦对了 太长你记不住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为笨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说我笨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就冯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯·霍恩海姆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯·霍恩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点倒是能记住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼写是…对了你会读书写字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会才怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会也能干活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴隶的活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不想得到自由和权利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想得到人类的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想一辈子当奴隶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是和永远困在这烧瓶里一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我赐给你知识吧 冯·霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你到底是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么称呼你才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧瓶中的小人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就叫我Homunculus（人造人）吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事万物都诞生于一 回归于一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即所谓 一即是全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全来自一 一中有全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若一中无全 全即为无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是出色的炼金术师了 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还只是个助手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本比不上主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你给了我知识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能过上这样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也感谢主人的提拔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天结婚成家也不是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是不便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样保持社群进行繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法存续种族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么繁殖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你看来可能很可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有家庭有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类才会感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的幸福又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不奢求什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从这烧瓶里出来就算幸福了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么达到权利和荣耀顶峰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会追求这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是在陛下面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢犯上我就把烧瓶摔碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想要毁掉未知的知识之源吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别啰嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老 到底能否实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衰老的焦虑吗 真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克塞尔克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就教你们长生不老的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灌溉用的水道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王下令在全国铺设水路网
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是克塞尔克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们平民也关怀备至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 一个不留全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧把血之纹刻上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北边村子被袭击了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是一个活口都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前是西边的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁干的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下期待的炼成阵已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漫长啊 终于好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样就可以长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王可以长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是划时代的瞬间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我们在中心不会被波及的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼成阵真正的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你所站的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用自己体内你的血打开了门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血脉相容的亲人 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你我就是一切的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅西蒂尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱茵迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 梅悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 所有人的魂魄都被抽走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 您没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…我自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据你的血的信息 我做了自己的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 终于可以用自己的脚走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是人造人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你提供血液的回报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给了你名字 给了你知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 还给了你不朽的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不朽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在心中集中意识试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你成为不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为代价的这个国家所有人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其中一半我用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的协助 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你就是爱德和阿尔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到你竟是我儿子们的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 你太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹密女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹密 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就拿药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微懂点医术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希格先生 请去叫辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹密女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到真理了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你牺牲了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内脏被取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要唤醒死去的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹密 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刺穿了你的肚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我呼吸顺畅多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被取走的内脏是你的罪证 所以拿不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我稍微整理了一下你的内脏系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让血液循环顺畅一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹密女士 你现在还不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆 你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有名为冯·霍恩海姆之人形的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲学者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上石 大炼金药
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石 就像它有很多名字一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其形态也不一定是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科先生拿的是半液体状的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利拿的是矿石状的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小大概这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说是具有巨大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为会更大才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没见过比小石头更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果是很大的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就需要不计其数的人来当材料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是尽量不想看到
Comment: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了获得什么 必须付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是炼金术之原理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是人世的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第41话 地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真在少年身上寻求的代价便是伤痛
